replyContent: The color changes in the PARAVOX Logo and the lights beside the logo represent the status of the ITC process. Red=Scanning Yellow=Change in sensor data/possible hit, Blue= ITC Process has a result. Thank you for your feedback!

content: It started saying random words even when I didn't ask questions. None which made sense. Correct me if I'm wrong someone and I would gladly change my opinion.
replyContent: Thank you for your feedback! The word ITC feature relies on your phone sensors, in a 6 step process. A spirit/entity can manipulate the picked words at every step. If there is no connection to a spirit for manipulation, random words can be shown. The key is to find a connection between a spirit/entity for communication.
